   Mildbr. (Zambia) and F. variifolia Warb. (Gabon). Allotriozoon
   nigeriense Wiebes was collected in Cameron from Ficus chlamydocarpa
   Mildbr. and Burret. Platyscapa desertorum Compton (Cape Province, host
   Ficus c. cordata Thunb.), Nigeriella excavata Compton (Transvaal, host
   Ficus tettensis Hutch.), Courtella wardi Compton (Natal, host Ficus t.
   tremula Warb.) and C. malawi Wiebes (Malawi, host Ficus chirindinensis
   Berg) are described as new species. A check-list is presented of the
