   Mathithumilan, Balachandran; Kadam, Niteen Narharirao; Reddy, Sowmya H.; Ankaiah, Mahadeva; Narayanan, Madhura J.; Makarla, Udayakumar; Sreeman, Sheshshayee Madavalam, Univ Agr Sci Bangalore, Dept Crop Physiol, Bangalore, Karnataka, India.
